  Arabic localisation for the PayHub Merchant Android app.

  Labels are pulled from web/src/i18n/locales/ar.ts where the concept matches
  the SPA / PWA, so the operator / shopkeeper sees one consistent vocabulary
  across portal, web-app and native app. Android-only copy (the "Advanced"
  server-URL toggle, push-permission rationale, FCM channel name) is written
  fresh to match the app voice.
-->
